column5: worth the wait!   thanks to the guy fishing with the pop can and zara spook for taking the picture ( true story)
That there is one BIG goldfish!
o man that thing is LONG!  what are the lengths/weights? nice fish jamie i gotta go out and get myself a carp soontime
Victor, no weight or length onthat fish, it was about 36" and I am guessing 25-28 pounds
SWEEEEEEEEEEEET!!!!  The carp have disappeared in my neck of the woods....water levels are waaaaay down.  Good to see some reports with people doing some catching!
Guess I have to move back to Ottawa to continue my carp career. LOL  Nice fish, CH.
wow, nice catch! that's one big *bleeping* fish
Nice big carp! It's mother of all gold fish!
Great catch CH...You're so lucky to be living close to a monster factory.
